data.summary: Your hard drive is failing with many damaged spots, and your graphics driver is causing Xbox Game Bar to crash. This is serious and needs immediate attention.

Good news! Your graphics card is working fine and the driver is up to date. Everything looks healthy from what we checked.
Your internet is working fine! The confusing message about missing gateway is a false alarm because you're actually online with great speed.
